{"tid":1680350,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有無人想私了啲捉棋黨","createTime":"2019-10-28T18:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T02:19:25.000Z","uid":83648,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b646b46fd5b54b3f1549d889065db3cc1db5186d","tid":1680350,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢好擾民但警察又唔做嘢的話<br />\n我哋就唯有要親自郁手<br />\n<br />\n一來可以阻嚇蝗蟲嚟香港行騙，令佢哋驚<br />\n二來可以美化市容，驅逐啲蝗蟲叔<br />\n三來外畀觀感正面，因為係幫緊街坊光復<br />\n<br />\n行動<br />\n一遇到有捉棋黨<br />\n立即上連登報料求增援<br />\n現場見到有增援手足的話<br />\n就問：有無人想捉棋！<br />\n由於一般呢啲捉棋黨都三四個，<br />\n所以夠十個就可以兇佢或開波<br />\n唔使擔心唔夠人<br />\n因為佢哋一定開係旺區<br />\n例如朗豪坊對面或豉油街隧道<br />\n<br />\n每次見到班大陸哩圍埋一齊就好撚燥<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"925161dc4182891b1bb6828fe0060a92bcdd740f","tid":1680350,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41ffff22d6e8e2a5cc128cf796075d4a1f4ba14","tid":1680350,"uid":104032,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"好似專登搵戰線黎開...作用不大仲好難睇"},{"pid":"bb868ae2928ad158b5c8a8037be57f77b731a055","tid":1680350,"uid":127108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:21:56.000Z","msg":"想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ad5e66f9fac02de9d2b4e709af45842a086da0","tid":1680350,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:22:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇下啦，2、3樓都仲有資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得睇下<br />\n<br />\n【正視聽：反思行動及行動數量】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680287</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e25f23f97ebc4ff63c31fe34f78115f892efcdce","tid":1680350,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:22:06.000Z","msg":"即係本民前"},{"pid":"d726f999556fc528c33e2a714846c5f92437ce11","tid":1680350,"uid":167277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b41ffff22d6e8e2a5cc128cf796075d4a1f4ba14","tid":1680350,"uid":104032,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"好似專登搵戰線黎開...作用不大仲好難睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:23:47.000Z","msg":"agger,<br />\n唔覺得需要咁做"},{"pid":"ed2836c9164309883f37ed7be5b125b4e98d36dd","tid":1680350,"uid":129925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:25:54.000Z","msg":"仲有d大陸 乞衣"},{"pid":"c616206df29dd6819e8ae44060654c343e851158","tid":1680350,"uid":311238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:29:23.000Z","msg":"救人呀！！有手足想自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680356</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2cbd793a339396b26f186c999d7f95713480b22","tid":1680350,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b41ffff22d6e8e2a5cc128cf796075d4a1f4ba14","tid":1680350,"uid":104032,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"好似專登搵戰線黎開...作用不大仲好難睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:14:32.000Z","msg":"但係光復香港嘅原意就係要咁<br />\n同埋班捉棋黨係清唔走<br />\n<br />\n黑警唔搞唔使講<br />\n基本上最多都係食環票控<br />\n你根本只有私了先有阻嚇作用<br />\n<br />\n而家根本得香港人自己搞到<br />\n唔係開唔開戰線問題<br />\n係民生問題"},{"pid":"0c971be6be8e2eaaf8bed536bffa51ae18c07eb9","tid":1680350,"uid":218855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}